      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still firm and free of any wear or fading, and all electronic features functioning perfectly. It has been meticulously garaged and maintained, making it a rare find for a discerning buyer who expects the highest standard of quality.",
