    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been clearly well-cared for over the years. It drives smoothly and remains a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality ride. While you might find some minor, honest signs of use consistent with its age, it's a solid, well-maintained car that\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner today!",
