    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, providing a reliable driving experience. While the exterior is generally clean, you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and very light surface scratches consistent with careful use. The interior is clean and free of tears, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. All electronics and features are fully functional, making this a great choice for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks and drives great.",
