    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it! It\u2019s an absolute gem that\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection inside and out. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel. It drives like a dream and looks even better. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
